{
  "stem": "2916.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I have a very vivid recollection of that simply because I remember that we were put a hundred people to a train.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And a hundred was-- into a car, to a wagon-- and a hundred was horribly crowded.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we stood all day, and then in the evening, they said 30 more.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And those 30 more people who were squeezed in there were people with hair and with clothes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And we found out that they were Jews who had been working in a factory, in a special place in Krakow.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "So I know those were Schindler's people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And another thing, they had toothbrushes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And each of them had a bottle of water.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And from time to time, they would brush their teeth and rinse their mouths, and spit it out.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And we had no water to drink.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "We were dying.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "We were dying for water.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And these people, we were hoping they would share their water with us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "But they didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I understand that they knew that they cannot share it with 100 people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "It was impossible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "But for us, it was a painful realization.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And I-- when I read I was so sorry that my mother wasn't alive anymore because I wanted to tell her, Mommy, those were the Schindler people.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "We didn't know who they were.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And my mother just kept remembering for years and years that they brushed their teeth and spat the water out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "We would have gladly drunk what they spat out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "That's how the recollection-- my recollection of these people, all dressed up like people, and having toothbrushes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that camp, we did hard manual labor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We worked outdoors.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were leveling the hills because we were building more and more extensions to this camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was very, very hard labor.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
